                    <p><b>Course Synopsis: </b>Design and development of distributed networking system.</p><p><br></p><p><b>Goal:</b> The course covers about: the function and structure of communications sub-nets,</p><p>network architectures and their protocols, approaches to the organisation of sub-nets and their</p><p>architectures, processes of network and protocol design, role of network standards and their</p><p>relationship to products, Network OS, Distributed Object Network and advance applications.</p><div><br></div>
